### 1. 创建第一个商品 (MacBook)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemName": "MacBook Pro M3",
  "currentQuantity": 10
}

###
### 2. 查看所有商品 (验证是否创建成功)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

###
### 3. 执行入库 (给 ID 为 1 的商品加 50 件)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/stock-movements/inbound
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemId": 1,
  "amount": 50
}

###
### 4. 执行盘点 (发现实测只有 48 件)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/stocktakes?itemId=1&actualQuantity=48

### 5. 执行出库 (卖掉 10 台 MacBook)
# 预期结果：库存从 48 变成 38
POST http://localhost:8080/api/stock-movements/outbound
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemId": 1,
  "amount": 10
}

### 9. 更新商品基础信息
# 假设我们要把 ID 为 1 的商品改名
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemName": "MacBook Pro M3 Max (Updated)",
  "currentQuantity": 100
}